    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a> * <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">Score</a> * Lower Bound</b>\n</p><p>There are two semantics inside an <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> like search, related to <b>Lower Bounds</b>:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Alpha\" title=\"Alpha\">Alpha</a> is an <b>Lower Bound</b> of a <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">score</a> for this <a href=\"/Node\" title=\"Node\">node</a>.</li>\n<li> A <b>Lower Bound</b> is returned from an <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> like search, if it <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">fails high</a>. The <a href=\"/Node\" title=\"Node\">node</a> searched was a confirmed <a href=\"/Node_Types#CUT\" title=\"Node Types\">Cut-Node</a>. </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lower_Bound&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bound\" title=\"Bound\">Bound</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Exact_Score\" title=\"Exact Score\">Exact Score</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Integrated_Bounds_and_Values\" title=\"Integrated Bounds and Values\">Integrated Bounds and Values</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">Score</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Upper_Bound\" title=\"Upper Bound\">Upper Bound</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lower_Bound&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=152959\">Using just Upperbounds and Lowerbounds</a> by <a href=\"/Alvaro_Cardoso\" title=\"Alvaro Cardoso\">Alvaro Jose Povoa Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 01, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62913\">bound type in PVS&#160;?</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mahmoud_Uthman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mahmoud Uthman (page does not exist)\">Mahmoud Uthman</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Bound\" title=\"Bound\">Bound</a>, <a href=\"/Exact_Score\" title=\"Exact Score\">Exact Score</a>, <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lower_Bound&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Upper_and_lower_bounds\">Upper and lower bounds from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Branch_and_bound\">Branch-and-bound from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301150822\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 11/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTe